short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A free AI writer with ChatGPT to help you optimize your listing.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
**New Feature: Free Access to ChatGPT Plus, no OpenAi or ChatGPT Account needÔºÅ**
WalmartGPT is a free AI-powered listing optimizer that helps Walmart sellers optimize listing to improve Walmart search ranking. 
With the help of WalmartGPT, you will never need to search for Walmart tips or templates for your listings. Just one click, you can get some better listing choices by ChatGPT OpenAI. 

üöÄ Features
‚Äí Optimize title of Walmart listing
‚Äí Optimize description of Walmart listing
‚Äí Keywords finder and Keyword suggestion
‚Äí Copy optimized listing content with one click
‚Äí Export optimized listing content as .doc

üöÄ How to use
1. Optimize title
    a. Go to listing page of the product
    b. Open the WalmartGPT and select Title Generator
    c. Search and pick keywords
    d. Click Generate Title button and get suggestion.
2. Optimize description
    a. Go to listing page of the product
    b. Open the WalmartGPT and select Description Generator
    c. Search and select keywords, and set parameters.
    d. Click Generate Description and get suggestion.

üöÄ How it works
WalmartGPT analyzes current product information such as title, description, keywords and uses ChatGPT to provide you with optimized listing content.
